Directed by Shaad Ali

Written by Shaad Ali. Ananya Sharma

Cast Genelia D’Souza.Riteish Deshmukh.Mahesh Manjrekar. Darryl Bradford (Bus Passenger). Manoj Anand (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)).Karishma Kotak. Eve-Yasmine Saoud-Easton (Mike’s Mother). Atul Sharma (Ward Boy).Rakesh Bedi. Asha Patel (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Jayshree Panchal (Bus Passenger Lady). Parvinder Nandhra (School Principal). Bharat Mistri (Car Vomit Uncle). Leo Franky (Mike). Sarah Pitts (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Rajdeep Choudhury (Vishnu). Tom Murphy (Driving examiner). Mahbub Reza Chowdhury (Flowerman).Mohammed Husnain. Natasha Malik (Bus passenger). Agastya Gupta (Bodhi). Jai Patel (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Sikandar (Mister Lal). Shahan Chaudhry (Ward Boy). Anila Aslam (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Ajmal Adurker (Driving Instructor). Ian Macnaughton (The Gardener). Ayesha Ali (Bus Passenger). Sameera Shahid (Bus passanger). Peter Whitten (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Hiren Vyas (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Mario Whitten (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Adnan Kapadia (Pandit Ji). Khushi Vyas (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted)). Matt Campbell (Bus Passenger). Rajendrakumar Patel (Chupke Chupke Music Reveller (scenes deleted))

Language Hindi

Producers Shaad Ali. Siva Ananth. Mahbub Reza Chowdhury. Kartik R. Iyer. Priyesh Kaushik. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Sarwar Mohammad. Rohit Phale.

Production 4K Inc. Hectic Cinema. T-Series Films.
